beer.beer_description:
Fresh off winning a Gold at AIBAs for our Imperial NEIPA, we thought we'd make and everyday version.
The brewers are really happy with this base malt bill that gives this beer a consistent haze with a silky and juicy mouthfeel. This is supported by fruity and resinous nose and flavour supplied by more than 5 carefully selected hop varieties that delivers maximum aromas before the beer finishes cleanly with low bitterness.
